{"tid":2343338,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【動森成語廊】指鹿為馬","createTime":"2020-12-28T01:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T01:08:18.000Z","uid":129010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cf43a59cc222a374bbd91fbf54580867365baf03","tid":2343338,"uid":129010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T01:08:18.000Z","msg":"公元前210年，秦始皇回到咸陽發喪。大臣趙高等人改變秦始皇遺詔，轉立秦始皇的幼子胡亥為帝，是為秦二世皇帝。丞相趙高意圖謀反，但又怕群臣不服想出一個辦法，帶一隻鹿到朝上並説：「這是馬來的。」秦二世笑話：「丞相你搞甚麼，謂鹿為馬。」於是，趙高向身邊左右大臣詢問，有些默不出聲，有些為了巴結趙高而認是馬，也有一些指出是鹿。這個故事用來比喻有人刻意顛倒是非黑白。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3MMSX85h4bQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3MMSX85h4bQ&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd0wAUq3ZsepC89uAf1Ef2WI%3D&h=245647cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3MMSX85h4bQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://open.lbry.com/@fishsunsun:9/ACIdiomsBlackWhite:2?r=EshHzmtuwXcNeDfguG1uLgpk1E31xvUS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopen.lbry.com%2F%40fishsunsun%3A9%2FACIdiomsBlackWhite%3A2%3Fr%3DEshHzmtuwXcNeDfguG1uLgpk1E31xvUS&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd0wAUq3ZsepC89uAf1Ef2WI%3D&h=f8bf9ac7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://open.lbry.com/@fishsunsun:9/ACIdiomsBlackWhite:2?r=EshHzmtuwXcNeDfguG1uLgpk1E31xvUS</a><br />\n<br />\n口述影像提供<br />\n我係鯧鯧鯧，多謝您睇呢段片<br />\n歡迎來訂閲支持，跟推介比朋友！"}]}